title: Openstreetmap, Thueringen Waterways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Thueringen Waterways, Germany, 2008
description: This data, provided by Openstreetmaps, shows various waterways in the Thueringen administrative area in the country of Germany. Waterways include canals, rivers, streams, and other water bound transportation routes. Data was uploaded as a poly line shape file with attributes for Feature name, feature type, and feature width when available.
